4Geeks Academy offers a course called "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" that prepares students for a career in data science. The course is designed for beginners and takes 16 weeks to complete. Students will learn Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics, as well as how to create predictive models using libraries like Pandas and Numpy. The course covers topics such as close neighbors, decision trees, supervised and unsupervised learning models. Students will also have the opportunity to work on real-life case studies and develop their own AI projects. The course is taught by experienced instructors and classes have a maximum of 12 students. No previous experience is required. For more information, visit their website at https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop